{"body":{"coverUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/62","type":"VILLAGE_REPRESENTATIVE","status":"UNCURRENT","id":31,"name":"陳昀志","electorate":"彰化縣秀水鄉第一選區<br>安東、安溪、莊雅、秀水、金興、陝西","weight":3,"contact":"聯絡我們","support":"支持我們","politics":"政策","declaration":"讓遊子回到更好的家鄉","areaId":9,"areaName":"彰化縣","createdAt":"2022-05-28T08:58:36.533Z","candidateAttachments":[{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/872","id":685,"attachmentType":"url","attachmentUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9iLZX6jbLbw","attachmentName":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9iLZX6jbLbw&ab_channel=%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F2022%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89","title":"陳昀志_競選宣言","content":null,"weight":99,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T06:52:59.168Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/871","id":684,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/5.png","attachmentName":"4f03cece-aa18-4668-b658-c632c6bdb64e_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":5,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T06:52:22.228Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/870","id":683,"attachmentType":"image/jpeg","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/4.jpg","attachmentName":"be4fb927-f508-424c-9688-b5f8d536bb9c_.jpg","title":" ","content":null,"weight":4,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T06:52:21.661Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/869","id":682,"attachmentType":"image/jpeg","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/3.jpg","attachmentName":"28ef0789-a3a9-4055-a0ab-f86702a35238_.jpg","title":" ","content":null,"weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T06:52:21.472Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/868","id":681,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/2.png","attachmentName":"8f86e1dc-7891-4dfa-a102-32d03b7989f8_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T06:52:21.321Z"},{"attachmentUri":"https://2022.npp.vote/api/v1/attachment/867","id":680,"attachmentType":"image/png","attachmentUrl":"https://2022.npp.vote/public/uploads/1.png","attachmentName":"931997a3-967c-4f42-9398-a8ac905fb8a1_.png","title":" ","content":null,"weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-06-16T06:52:20.354Z"}],"candidateContacts":[{"id":45,"title":"電話","content":" 04-769-7074   0975 918 368 ","createdAt":"2022-06-01T01:46:59.794Z"},{"id":44,"title":"地址","content":"彰化縣秀水鄉金興村番花路284號","createdAt":"2022-06-01T01:46:15.770Z"}],"candidateDeclaration":{"id":28,"title":" ","content":"<p>秀水是酪農故鄉，這裡養著三千多頭乳牛，知名的飛牛牧場創辦人也是秀水子弟。秀水的豌豆產量在全國名列前茅，我的兒時記憶，就是騎腳踏車去牧場餵乳牛，以及跟著爺爺奶奶去市場賣豌豆。<br /><br />但秀水也跟許多鄉村一樣，面臨人口流失及發展停滯的問題，因此我這次站出來，就是希望能替在地青年發聲，改革青年最在意的議題。例如：近四萬人的秀水，卻面臨綠地空間不足、連結南北彰化重要道路的彰水路，卻有交通設計太過時的問題、以及水五金聚落造成的農地工廠汙染問題等等。<br /><br /><strong>我希望從基層一步一腳印的推動秀水的革新，讓離家的遊子們回家的時候，會發現故鄉變得更好，甚至會想回來家鄉。</strong></p>","createdAt":"2022-05-30T09:01:55.892Z"},"candidateEducations":[{"id":67,"title":"國立中正大學歷史系及政治系學士（雙主修）","content":null,"weight":0,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.706Z"}],"candidateExperiences":[{"id":140,"title":"立法委員陳椒華彰化服務處助理","content":null,"weight":0,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.766Z"}],"candidatePolitics":[{"id":158,"title":"創新政治","content":"推動代表會資訊公開透明化，讓鄉民了解每筆預算利用在何處，使代表會成為全民的代表會。","weight":7,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:37.116Z"},{"id":157,"title":"觀光秀水","content":"利用自行車道串連秀水各大景點及古蹟，結合休閒農業及牧業，連結鹿港及八卦山的觀光旅遊路線，使秀水不再只是路過的地方。","weight":6,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:37.057Z"},{"id":156,"title":"行的安全","content":"盤點鄉內主要幹道設計，改善易肇事路段肇事原因，爭取學區設置人行道，規劃全鄉自行車道。\n\n讓學生就學放學能受到最妥善保護，改善農路品質、耕耘期加強清除道路汙泥。","weight":5,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.999Z"},{"id":155,"title":"社區營造","content":"協助合作成立社區營造協會，組織社區巡守隊及環保志工隊，共創宜居社區環境。","weight":4,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.944Z"},{"id":154,"title":"老有所終","content":"成立社區關懷據點，創設銀髮才藝班、社區共餐服務、以及獨老關懷機制、讓爺爺奶奶不再宅在家，擁有自己的交友圈，共同編織出社會安全網。","weight":3,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.887Z"},{"id":153,"title":"壯有所用","content":"設立返鄉青年創業平台，提供青創資訊供秀水青年子弟交流使用，協助輔導及提供就業機會，讓遊子們能回鄉團圓。","weight":2,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.830Z"},{"id":152,"title":"幼有所長","content":"盤點鄉內幼托機構現況，確保每個父母都能找到良好且可靠的幼托環境。成立社區青少年課輔班，讓青少年放學後能受到妥善照顧。","weight":1,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.769Z"}],"candidateSocial":{"id":35,"line":null,"facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/yunchihxiushui","email":"ycchen0228@gmail.com","instagram":null,"youtube":null,"createdAt":"2022-06-03T03:04:15.819Z"},"candidateSupports":[{"id":62,"title":"看板和志工應援","content":" ","weight":0,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.836Z"},{"id":61,"title":"政治獻金專戶","content":" ","weight":0,"createdAt":"2022-05-30T08:58:36.778Z"}]}}